snippet.title: Best VGM 907 - Mushihimesama Futari - On the Verge of Madness ~ Stage 5
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade / Xbox 360
Mushihimesama Futari (2007)
On the Verge of Madness ~ Stage 5
Miho Nakamura
